  "text": "Content validity. 17 features were automatically selected based on the recorded data alone. For all features we calculated Pearson's correlation coe cient \u21e2 2 and the maximal information coe cient (MIC) [CITATION_1] between the feature and the test score to measure the linear and non-linear relationships, respectively. For most features the relationship is highly non-linear, which prohibits the use of simple ",
